This program it's licensed under GPL 


Compilation:

mkdir build && cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr ..
make 
sudo make install

Features:

> Themes installation
> Themes uninstallation
> Icon themes selection
> Icon themes fallback selection
> themes selection
> fonts selection

enjoy !


ChangeLog:
